    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>LEAD: The Ogilvy Group has reached an agreement to purchase Thomson-Leeds, a point-of-sale advertising company, and Alert Marketing, an in-store merchandising and sales organization. They will become part of a newly created Sales Promotion Group, part of Sage Worldwide.</p>
